OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOften cloudy
OL,6,FThursday evening and overnight with
OL,7,Fpatchy rain and drizzle, particularly
OL,8,Ffurther west and north. A band of
OL,9,Fheavier rain then arriving into the
OL,10,Fwest as dawn approaches. Winds
OL,11,Fgenerally increasing, becoming
OL,12,Fblustery along exposed coasts and high
OL,13,Fground.
OL,14,
OL,15,CFriday:FA cloudy start with a band of
OL,16,Frain gradually spreading eastward,
OL,17,Fclearing most parts by afternoon.
OL,18,FTurning drier and brighter from the
OL,19,Fwest once cleared, with winds
OL,20,Fgradually easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
