OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,6,Flargely fine and dry weekend, with an
OL,7,Fisolated shower possible Saturday.
OL,8,FFeeling pleasant in any sunshine with
OL,9,Flighter winds. Likely to remain
OL,10,Fsimilar on Monday as high pressure
OL,11,Fdominates.
